CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 5, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Love, Honor - Miss Edna Snell of Coraopolis, and Henry Robinson of Pittsburgh were married May 1, by the Rev. William Wilson. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Henry Robinson wearing pinstriped double breasted suit, and Edna Snell Robinson wearing gown with feather and bow pattern, and necklace of two strands of pearl or beads, posed in domestic interior in Coraopolis
